    "description": "Hidden-bisect now accepts --batch-decode-full-attn-row-chunk-size, records the row-chunk size in workload metadata, forwards HIPENGINE_QWEN35_BATCH_DECODE_FULL_ATTN_ROW_CHUNK_SIZE, and labels rowchunk traces as native_batch_row_chunks/non-native-caware. The runtime now traces each native full-attention row chunk scratch/MoE payload in order so hidden-bisect can concatenate chunk traces instead of failing on partial-row trace shapes."
